Package: featuretablefilter
Title: Feature Table Filtering for Microbiome Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vojtech", "Barton", email = "vojtech.barton@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for filtering microbiome feature tables based on coverage, abundance,
    and network connectivity. Supports phyloseq and TreeSummarizedExperiment objects natively.
